---
---

<section id="about" class="section">
  <div class="section-header animate-on-scroll">
    <h2 class="section-title"><span class="prompt">$</span> cat about.md</h2>
    <div class="section-underline"></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="about-bio animate-on-scroll">
    <div class="terminal-card-header">
      <span class="dot"></span>
      <span class="prompt">bio.txt</span>
    </div>
    <p>I am a person who always thinks out original things. I require my friends to be honest in purpose, honest in speech, as well as in money affairs. My greatest weakness lies in the way I treat others. I believe it is well worth trying at any stage of life. When confronted with obstacles, I stay calm and rational and work on finding a solution. This calmness is sometimes seen as being cold and calculating.</p>
    
    <p>I can analyze and solve complex problems. I am never still and always make plans and the thing I can least tolerate is inactivity. In very tough situations as well, I keep amazing patience. I am ambitious and always ready to take the risk. With all my patience and faith, I wait for the right time. I never get stressed due to hurdles. I have much self-will, and the spirit of independence is firmly planted in me.</p>
    
    <p>I have the bump of acquisition strongly developed. It follows that I like to collect things — old books, old parts of automotive, computers, electronics, etc. Moreover, I find throwing things away or parting with them very difficult. I always think that I may want these someday and thus, I am a born collector.</p>
    
    <p>Other hobbies revolve around virtualization and I always virtualize any new Operating System, Network Monitoring tool, Firewalls like Cisco IOS, JunOS, PFsense and XG Firewalls.</p>
    
    <p>I have the patience to make things, and if I have not the skill I could easily acquire it. A highly motivated individual with experience in managing Enterprise-class networks, SME's, GOV and Financial bodies.</p>
    
    <p>Areas of interest include DevOps and Infrastructure automation. Currently equipping myself to learn all the core competencies to become a successful DevOps Engineer.</p>
    
    <span class="about-bio-cite">— Veera.K</span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="about-cards">
    <div class="terminal-card animate-on-scroll">
      <div class="terminal-card-header">
        <span class="dot"></span>
        <span class="prompt">> more_about.sh</span>
      </div>
      <div class="terminal-card-body">
        <ul class="about-card-list">
          <li>My life started with curiosity. But soon my rest was arrested as per the tradition — 5 to 17 school and 18 to 21 college. In between these I made out a special place for my ideas and innovations which will make a mark in the real world.</li>
          <li>I started working as a freelancer during my college and soon started getting regular income through various verticals like Database, Networking and Website Designing.</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="about-card-socials">
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/TheVeeraKumar" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="social-link" aria-label="LinkedIn">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433a2.062 2.062 0 01-2.063-2.065 2.064 2.064 0 112.063 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="terminal-card animate-on-scroll">
      <div class="terminal-card-header">
        <span class="dot"></span>
        <span class="prompt">> what_i_do.sh</span>
      </div>
      <div class="terminal-card-body">
        <ul class="about-card-list">
          <li>Experience in handling production systems and excellent troubleshooting skills</li>
          <li>Experience with logging and monitoring systems like ELK, Graylog, Grafana, Newrelic, Nagios</li>
          <li>Experience managing web servers like Nginx/Apache, technologies like Java/Python/Ruby & tuning/troubleshooting databases like MySQL</li>
          <li>Experience in bash & other scripting languages like Python</li>
          <li>Experience in CI/CD & build systems like Jenkins</li>
          <li>Experience in AWS services like EC2, RDS, S3, etc.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="terminal-card animate-on-scroll">
      <div class="terminal-card-header">
        <span class="dot"></span>
        <span class="prompt">> pipeline.sh</span>
      </div>
      <div class="terminal-card-body">
        <ul class="about-card-list">
          <li>Certification of DevOps Engineer</li>
          <li>Contribute to Open Source Security Solutions</li>
          <li>Deployment of Infrastructure as a Code</li>
          <li>Let's Collaborate or give me a shout on GitHub & Stack Overflow</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
    entries.forEach((entry) => {
      if (entry.isIntersecting) {
        setTimeout(() => {
          entry.target.classList.add('animated');
        }, 100);
        observer.unobserve(entry.target);
      }
    });
  }, { threshold: 0.1 });

  document.querySelectorAll('.animate-on-scroll').forEach(el => {
    observer.observe(el);
  });
</script>
